    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Calm是初始状态。当EdgeNode通过IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker检测到玩家时，就切换到Aggressive追击状态。如果追击过程中丢失目标，由IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic判断后进入Alerted警戒状态。",
