    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下：Calm通过MQTT检测到玩家进入Aggressive；Aggressive丢失目标后进入Alerted。那Alerted之后呢？怎么回到Calm？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alerted",
