      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Alerted有两个出口：一是cooldown elapsed，冷却时间结束后回到Calm；二是player seen again，重新发现玩家则回到Aggressive。另外每个状态我需要标注NPCPathSystem的具体行为。",
