      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "状态结构已经画好了。现在我在右侧添加注释：Calm状态是patrols between nodes加random idle 3-5s；Aggressive状态标注chases player，来源是IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode；Alerted状态是goes to last seen position。这样准确吗？",
